  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink36-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">tāṉ vāyiṉēruṅ kuṟippiṉaḷāṉamai aṟiyātu tōḻi vāyil maṟuttuḻi avaḷ nērum
          vakaiyāl avaṭkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink36">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi yūra</l>
          <l> ṉammaṟan tamaikuva ṉāyi ṉāmaṟan</l>
          <l> tuḷḷā tamaitalu mamaikuva maṉṉē</l>
          <l> kayaleṉak karutiya vuṇkaṇ</l>
          <l> pacalaik kolkā vākutal peṟiṉē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> Alas, [my] friend!</l>
          <l> If the man from the village</l> 
          <l> is happy to forget us, [then] we will forget [him],</l>
          <l>not think [of him]–</l>
          <l> and our carp-like black kajal-eyes</l> 
          <l> will be quite happy to forget and not think [of him]– </l>
          <l> unless they grow weak from pallor.</l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
